{"lemma":"عَتَبَةٌ","slug":"عَتَبَةٌ","root":"ع.ت.ب","root_slug":"ع-ت-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ت-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27930"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"threshold, doorsill"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕa.ta.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27930","headword_ar":"عَتَبَةٌ","root":"Etb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usokuf~ap","text_ar":"اُسْكُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"threshold"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a door, (S, A, Mgh, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which one treads:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper of the two"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transverse pieces of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a door-way,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof each is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usokuf~ap","text_ar":"اُسْكُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lintel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) [for it is said that] the upper [piece of wood] in a door-way is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eatabap","text_ar":"عَتَبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the piece of wood that is above this is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjib","text_ar":"حَاجِب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Az, TA in this art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hjb","text_ar":"حجب"},{"kind":"text","text":";) and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^usokuf~ap","text_ar":"اُسْكُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the lowest [or threshold]; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAriDataAni","text_ar":"عَارِضَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaAdataAni","text_ar":"عِضَادَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or two side-posts]: (TA:) the pl. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabN","text_ar":"عَتَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[improperly termed a pl., for it is a coll. gen. n.,] (S, O, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabaAtN","text_ar":"عَتَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [It is mostly used in the former of the two senses expl. above.] ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wife"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thus termed, (O, K,) metonymically, in like manner as she is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEolN","text_ar":"نَعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c. (O.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A step; a single step of a series:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single step of a series made of wood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabN","text_ar":"عَتَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[improperly termed a pl., as observed above,] (S, O, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabaAtN","text_ar":"عَتَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEatabataAni","text_ar":"العَتَبَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two thresholds"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lintels"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"steps"},{"kind":"text","text":"] termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxaArijapu","text_ar":"الخَارِجَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the outer"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aAxilapu","text_ar":"الدَّاخِلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the inner"},{"kind":"text","text":"] are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two wellknown figures of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the science of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~amol","text_ar":"الرَّمْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"geomancy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eatabapu waAdK","text_ar":"عَتَبَةُ وَادٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The extreme side of a valley, that is next the mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEtbp","text_ar":"العتبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEatabapu","text_ar":"العَتَبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", supposed by Freytag to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEutobapu","text_ar":"العُتْبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of bending of the valley."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 18.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabapN","text_ar":"عَتَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hardship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hateful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disagreeable, thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"event;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabN","text_ar":"عَتَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humila fulaAnN EalaY","text_ar":"حُمِلَ فُلَانٌ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabapK","text_ar":"عَتَبَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was incited, urged, induced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made, to do,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to suffer, a disagreeable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hateful, thing, of a trying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an afflictive, kind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Al$~ar~i","text_ar":"مِنَ الشَّرِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Humila EalaY EatabK","text_ar":"حُمِلَ عَلَى عَتَبٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabapK","text_ar":"عَتَبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was incited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to suffer, a hardship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiY h`*aA AlA^amori","text_ar":"مَا فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA ratabN","text_ar":"وَلَا رَتَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabN","text_ar":"عَتَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in this thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, any hardship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EatabaAtu Almawoti","text_ar":"عَتَبَاتُ المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The severities"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pains"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agonies"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}